---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Firecrawl MCP — Julien Klein">
  <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;">
    <div style="padding: 3rem 0 1rem;">
      <a href="/ressources" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #8B7355;">← Ressources</a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #A85C3A; border: 1px solid #A85C3A; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 999px;">MCP</span> <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #8B7355; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 999px;">Scraping</span></div>
    <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; color: #2C2416;">Firecrawl</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: #8B7355; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">Scraping web avancé directement depuis Claude. Firecrawl gère les pages JavaScript, les sites derrière authentification, Notion, et les PDFs. Utilisé dans <code>/ingest</code> pour transformer n'importe quelle URL en contenu structuré.</p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
      <div style="padding: 1.2rem; background: #FAF7F2; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 10px;">
        <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Cas d'usage</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416; line-height: 1.6;">Ingérer des articles, benchmarks concurrents, pages Notion partagées, rapports PDF, threads Twitter.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 1.2rem; background: #FAF7F2; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 10px;">
        <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Installation</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416; line-height: 1.6;">Clé API Firecrawl requise. Ajout via <code>claude mcp add -s user</code> avec la variable <code>FIRECRAWL_API_KEY</code>.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2C2416;">Ce que Firecrawl sait faire</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0;">
      {[
        "Scraper des pages JavaScript (React, Next.js, SPAs)",
        "Passer derrière certaines authentifications (cookies)",
        "Extraire le texte propre d'un PDF",
        "Crawler tout un domaine (plusieurs pages en cascade)",
        "Retourner du Markdown structuré prêt pour le Second Brain"
      ].map((step, i) => (
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline; padding: 0.7rem 0; border-top: 1px solid #D4C9B5;">
          <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #8B7355; font-family: monospace; flex-shrink: 0;">{String(i+1).padStart(2,'0')}</span>
          <span style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416;">{step}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 5rem;">
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Skills qui l'utilisent</div>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
        <a href="/ressources/skills/ingest" style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 6px; color: #2C2416;">/ingest →</a>
        <a href="/ressources/skills/capture" style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 6px; color: #2C2416;">/capture →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
